IDS
Intrusion Detection System passively monitors on a network and also can perform advanced checks such as protocol and content inspection
 Types
>HIDS(host IDS)
works with a software agent on a host

>NIDS(n/w IDS)
monitors multiple hosts
gain access to network traffic my connecting to a network switch which is configures for port mirroring or a network tap

>Signature Based
monitors network packets and compares them with a preconfigured patterns known as signatures

>Anomaly Based
Creates a basline based of normal network traffic;current network traffic is compared with the baseline to detect any spikes in the bandwidth usage
 
IPS
Intrusion Protection System
combines the functions of a IDS and firewall ,it peforms In-depth inspection and uses this information to block possible attacks

